name: Manowixie #001 - LunaPix
description: Derek and his “cat” Steve. They have been living amongst us for many years, undetected, until now. With each one we discover, we learn more. Fact find pt1: shocking to look at by us humans, but not for long as their wide stare seems to have a hypnotic effect on us, making us remember them as a dream instead of real life.
